---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="GJ 667Cc Colony"
  description="GJ 667Cc -- the first world to receive a breathable atmosphere via atmospheric processing. Class A major hub with 500,000+ residents. A flagship of Weyland-Yutani terraforming capability."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          CLASS A -- MAJOR HUB -- FLAGSHIP COLONY
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-[10rem] font-black text-white mb-4 leading-none uppercase">
          GJ <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">667CC</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-6"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          FIRST BREATHABLE ATMOSPHERE -- SINCE 2039
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Colony Data Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">LOCATION</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">GJ 667CC</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">SYSTEM</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">GLIESE 667</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">BREATHABLE SINCE</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">2039</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">POPULATION</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">500,000+</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">STATUS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] status-active">OPERATIONAL</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Historic Achievement Banner -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#FFC600]/5 border-b-2 border-[#FFC600]/20 py-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#FFC600] animate-pulse-yellow"></span>
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
            HISTORIC ACHIEVEMENT -- FIRST SUCCESSFUL PLANETARY ATMOSPHERE CONVERSION -- PROOF OF CONCEPT FOR ALL SUBSEQUENT TERRAFORMING
          </span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#FFC600] animate-pulse-yellow"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
                COLONY OVERVIEW
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8">
                THE PROOF THAT <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">BUILDING BETTER WORLDS</span> IS MORE THAN A SLOGAN
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> GJ 667CC HOLDS A SINGULAR DISTINCTION IN HUMAN HISTORY: IT IS THE FIRST WORLD BEYOND EARTH TO RECEIVE A FULLY BREATHABLE ATMOSPHERE THROUGH ENGINEERED ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSING. WHEN THE FIRST COLONIST STEPPED OUTSIDE WITHOUT A RESPIRATOR IN 2039, IT MARKED THE MOMENT HUMANITY PROVED IT COULD PERMANENTLY ALTER WORLDS TO SUSTAIN LIFE.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> WHAT BEGAN AS A WEYLAND CORPORATION TERRAFORMING DEMONSTRATION HAS GROWN INTO ONE OF THE MOST VIBRANT AND FULLY DEVELOPED COLONY WORLDS IN EXISTENCE. WITH A POPULATION EXCEEDING HALF A MILLION, GJ 667CC IS A COMPLETE CIVILIZATION WITH AGRICULTURE, HEAVY INDUSTRY, EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS, CULTURAL CENTERS, AND A SELF-SUSTAINING ECONOMY.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE COLONY SERVES AS THE LIVING PROOF OF WEYLAND-YUTANI'S CORE MISSION. EVERY TECHNOLOGY, EVERY PROCESS, AND EVERY OPERATIONAL METHODOLOGY DEVELOPED ON GJ 667CC HAS BEEN REFINED AND DEPLOYED ACROSS HUNDREDS OF SUBSEQUENT COLONY WORLDS. THIS IS WHERE THE TEMPLATE FOR HUMAN INTERSTELLAR CIVILIZATION WAS WRITTEN.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b-2 border-[#FFC600] pb-3">COLONY SPECIFICATIONS</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">DESIGNATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">GJ 667CC COLONY</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">SYSTEM</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">GLIESE 667 (TRIPLE STAR)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">ATMOSPHERE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">BREATHABLE (ENGINEERED)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">FIRST BREATH</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">2039</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">POPULATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">500,000+</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">GRAVITY</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">1.03 G</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">AGRICULTURE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">SELF-SUFFICIENT</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">ECONOMY</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">DIVERSIFIED / MATURE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">GOVERNANCE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">W-Y COLONIAL ADMIN</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sectors of Development -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            DEVELOPMENT
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            A COMPLETE <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">CIVILIZATION</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 uppercase font-mono tracking-wider">FULLY DEVELOPED ACROSS EVERY SECTOR OF SOCIETY</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">AG</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">AGRICULTURE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              SELF-SUFFICIENT AGRICULTURAL SECTOR SPANNING OVER 40,000 HECTARES OF CULTIVATED LAND. GRAIN PRODUCTION, LIVESTOCK, AQUACULTURE, AND CONTROLLED-ENVIRONMENT FARMING PRODUCE A FOOD SURPLUS THAT IS EXPORTED TO DEVELOPING COLONIES.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">IN</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">INDUSTRY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              DIVERSIFIED INDUSTRIAL BASE INCLUDING MATERIALS MANUFACTURING, COMPONENT FABRICATION, VEHICLE ASSEMBLY, AND ATMOSPHERIC PROCESSOR PRODUCTION. THE COLONY MANUFACTURES EQUIPMENT DEPLOYED ACROSS DOZENS OF OTHER WORLDS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">ED</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">EDUCATION</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              A COMPLETE EDUCATIONAL SYSTEM FROM PRIMARY THROUGH TERTIARY. THE WEYLAND-YUTANI INSTITUTE OF COLONIAL SCIENCES, LOCATED ON GJ 667CC, IS THE PREMIER OFF-WORLD UNIVERSITY, PRODUCING THE ENGINEERS AND ADMINISTRATORS WHO BUILD NEW COLONIES.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">HC</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">HEALTHCARE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              THREE MAJOR MEDICAL CENTERS, TWELVE REGIONAL CLINICS, AND A DEDICATED RESEARCH HOSPITAL. ADVANCED MEDPOD SYSTEMS AND FULL SURGICAL CAPABILITIES. LIFE EXPECTANCY ON GJ 667CC EXCEEDS THE EARTH AVERAGE.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">CU</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">CULTURE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              MUSEUMS, PERFORMANCE VENUES, SPORTS FACILITIES, AND PUBLIC PARKS. GJ 667CC HAS DEVELOPED ITS OWN DISTINCT COLONIAL CULTURE WHILE MAINTAINING DEEP CONNECTIONS TO EARTH'S HERITAGE. THE COLONY HOSTS THE ANNUAL FRONTIER ARTS FESTIVAL.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">GV</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">GOVERNANCE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              A MATURE COLONIAL ADMINISTRATION WITH ELECTED ADVISORY COUNCILS OPERATING UNDER THE WEYLAND-YUTANI COLONIAL CHARTER. JUDICIARY, LAW ENFORCEMENT, INFRASTRUCTURE MANAGEMENT, AND PUBLIC SERVICES ALL FUNCTION INDEPENDENTLY.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Economic Stats -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              ECONOMY
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
              ECONOMIC <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">PROFILE</span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">$2.8T</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">ANNUAL GDP</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">98.2%</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">EMPLOYMENT</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">40K</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">HA CULTIVATED</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-2">12</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest">TRADE PARTNERS</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="terminal mt-16">
            <div class="terminal-content">
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                &gt; "GJ 667CC IS NOT MERELY A COLONY. IT IS A CIVILIZATION. WHEN PETER WEYLAND SPOKE OF BUILDING BETTER WORLDS, THIS IS WHAT HE ENVISIONED: A PLACE WHERE HUMAN BEINGS LIVE, WORK, RAISE FAMILIES, CREATE ART, PURSUE KNOWLEDGE, AND BUILD FUTURES ON A WORLD THAT WAS ONCE BARREN ROCK AND TOXIC ATMOSPHERE. EVERYTHING WE HAVE ACCOMPLISHED SINCE BEGAN HERE."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <section class="relative py-12 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/colonies" class="btn-secondary">ALL COLONIES</a>
          <a href="/colonies/luna" class="btn-secondary">LUNA COLONY</a>
          <a href="/careers" class="btn-primary">RELOCATE TO GJ 667CC</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
